title: Reno & The Doc (1984 Comedy) directed by Charles Dennis | Alpine action

sources.title: Reno & The Doc (1984 Comedy) directed by Charles Dennis | Alpine action
sources.description:
Two stubborn old men; ski rebel Reno (Kenneth Welsh), partners with Doc (Henry Ramer) to race through frosty peaks to intercept a slippery scheme. With wits sharper than ski edges, they outmaneuver surprise moves before this powder pursuit spins out of control.

Director & Writer: Charles Dennis
Actors: Kenneth Welsh, Henry Ramer, Gene Mack, Brian Grandbois,
Genres: Comedy, Drama, Sport
Release date: June 3, 1984
